messages.content: I see you're curious about the minimum deposit! The minimum deposit amount to start playing the game is RM10. Just make a quick deposit, and you'll be all set to enjoy our games! Happy gaming!

user_inputs.cleaned_prompt: How do I make a deposit?
user_inputs.generation: Dear Player, to make a deposit, please go to the deposit section on the app. You will find various payment methods available. Select your preferred method, enter the required details, and confirm the transaction. Your funds should be available shortly after the deposit is processed.

translations.text: Dear Player, to make a deposit, please go to the deposit section on the app. You will find various payment methods available. Select your preferred method, enter the required details, and confirm the transaction. Your funds should be available shortly after the deposit is processed.

Pemain yang dihormati, untuk membuat deposit, sila pergi ke bahagian deposit di aplikasi. Anda akan menemui pelbagai kaedah pembayaran yang tersedia. Pilih kaedah pilihan anda, masukkan butiran yang diperlukan dan sahkan transaksi tersebut. Dana anda sepatutnya tersedia sejurus selepas deposit diproses.
亲爱的玩家，若要进行存款，请您前往应用程序中的存款区域。您会发现多种可用的支付方式。请选择您偏好的方式，输入所需的详细信息，并确认交易。存款处理后，您的资金应会很快到账。
